{"tid":2170460,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"是否應該分手？","createTime":"2020-08-23T09:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T15:43:53.000Z","uid":7772,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d573770ba57c16172f9a22967a5e531ed0cdf7b1","tid":2170460,"uid":7772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:41:47.000Z","msg":"同女朋友拍左拖差唔多一年幾<br />\n平時生活無事既時候 的確上係好開心<br />\n相處上面 所有事都要我就哂佢 <br />\n佢一肚餓 一悶 就一定要所有野都幫佢做哂<br />\n諗唔到食咩即屌 食到佢唔想食既屌<br />\n放假無街出又屌 出街行得耐又屌<br />\n我唔可以去所有朋友既聚會 因為佢會悶親<br />\n就算帶佢去我朋友聚會都好 佢都會西哂面咁要走<br />\n但可以屌我唔介紹佢比我朋友識 <br />\n佢都會因為好小事而嬲我 例如我食野果陣 食左最後一舊無比佢<br />\n或者佢生痱「之」我唔記得帶藥膏比佢 我即刻衝去買 佢都要屌到我仆街<br />\n慢慢落黎 我覺得自己做既所有野都係錯 淨係識講對唔住<br />\n咁樣既生活好辛苦 我係咪應該要分手"},{"pid":"a8db55867af125eda815a9d89cb9ea16f927d3b4","tid":2170460,"uid":61722,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"你係佢隻狗多過係佢男朋友"},{"pid":"c528d072e918f16158fa55a28ad0e3341f44383e","tid":2170460,"uid":9392,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"分囉屌你老母臭西問問問"},{"pid":"11cc2585a6c69f153628140a6a31181ee4067349","tid":2170460,"uid":90664,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pPDkNJ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpPDkNJ5.jpg&h=f0294e8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d7329e3743b02eee2ce7a2344fc983a9eebfb2b","tid":2170460,"uid":256204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"感情問題一律分手.jpg"},{"pid":"9c7d65e9c998267ff0c4ecb71f457154d913eeb7","tid":2170460,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:45:06.000Z","msg":"你只係性奴"},{"pid":"9a0adc32de04bd56507ef8ef9da2bb6d2b2d6f9f","tid":2170460,"uid":128741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"內文都唔駛睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分手"}